---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profile from '../assets/images/pfp.jpg';
---
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 md:py-48">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-32 items-center">
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-text-primary leading-tight mb-8">
        Capturing the intersection of architecture and human experience.
      </h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-text-secondary space-y-6 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Based in the intersection of structural precision and organic life, Pax Pictora explores the quiet dialogue between built environments and the people who inhabit them. Every frame is an exercise in documentary authenticity, rejecting artificial lighting in favor of the raw, unyielding truth of natural illumination.
        </p>
        <p>
          The approach is deeply rooted in architectural appreciation, prioritizing clean lines, profound stillness, and the luxurious emptiness of negative space. We believe that true elegance lies not in what is added, but in what is deliberately stripped away.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
      <div class="aspect-3/4 w-full overflow-hidden bg-surface animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
        <Image 
          src={profile} 
          alt="About Pax Pictora" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
